extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
scan_protocol: Standard Affymetrix procedures using Gene ChIP Scanner 3000.
description: Gene expression data of sporadic colon cancer patient (INTcartella:2014274, INTistologico:299140I)
data_processing: RMA implementation of Affymetrix Power Tools version 1.8.6 was used to analyze the 'core' subset of probes (HuEx-1_0-st-v2.r2.dt1.hg18.core.mps). All additional analysis was performed in R/Bioconductor and is available as a reproducible Sweave document from <http://pierotti.group.ifom-ieo-campus.it/suppl/crc.html>.
contact_institute: Fondazione Istituto FIRC di Oncologia Molecolare
